    "description": "<blockquote style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px 0.5em 10px;padding:0px 0px 0px 10px !important;border-left:3px solid var(--color-border-light-tertiary);font-style:italic;font-size:16px;font-family:'EB Garamond', sans-serif !important;line-height:1.45em;color:rgb(43, 74, 66);font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-family: 'EB Garamond', sans-serif !important; font-style: italic; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.45em\"><span style=\"font-family: 'EB Garamond', sans-serif !important\"><em><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered the <strong>Ritualist </strong>Class.</em></span></p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin: 0px; font-family: 'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.45em; color: rgb(43, 74, 66); font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">Whenever you <strong>Rest</strong>, you may create a <strong>Mana Link</strong> between yourself and a willing ally. All previous <strong>Mana Links</strong> are lost when you create a new one. The <strong>Mana Link</strong> is also lost if either part of the link dies.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">While the <strong>Mana Link</strong> remains active, both of you gain the following benefits as long as you are able to see or hear each-other:</span></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"font-family: 'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">When you <strong>Cast a Spell</strong>, you may choose one from that ally’s list of spells.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: 'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">When you <strong>recover MP</strong>, you may instead recover half as much <strong>MP</strong> and have that ally recover the other half.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-family: 'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">When that ally <strong>spends or loses MP</strong>, you may pay up to <strong>half</strong> of that cost.</span></p></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-family: 'PT Sans Narrow', sans-serif\">If one of you uses any of the benefits from <strong>Mana Link</strong>, the other may use it until the current action or effect is fully resolved.</span></p>",
